<p class=3D"eqbodytext1"><span lang=3D"EN-GB" style=3D"font-size:12.0pt; fo=
nt-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">Tips Music reported strong 4QFY26=
 earnings growth of 92.9% YoY, driven by 32.4% revenue growth (19.1%/10.7%/=
21.4% in 1Q/2Q/3QFY26) and ~2,660bps EBIT margin
 expansion. Top-line growth was supported by sustained traction in the comp=
any=92s catalogue, particularly its 90s repertoire, with management reitera=
ting that growth was entirely recurring with no one-offs. Paid subscription=
 contribution has inched up to 10=9615%
 of digital revenue (10=9612% last year). Margin expansion was largely led =
by lower content spends (down 54.6% YoY) due to deferment of a key movie-ba=
sed music content release to 1QFY27. We broadly factor in management=92s re=
venue guidance of ~20% revenue growth
 in FY27 (up from 15% expected earlier) but build content spends at the low=
er end of the guidance of INR 800mn-900mn basis historical under-delivery. =
Overall, we raise FY27E=9628E EPS by 12=9615%. We roll-forward to Mar=9227 =
TP for a revised TP of INR 730 (INR 580
 earlier) as we now value the stock at 32x P/E versus 30x earlier.</span><s=
pan style=3D"font-size:12.0pt; font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">=
</span></p>
